    "name": "Chess Infinity: 大王棋盘套装",
    "steam_appid": 3311930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311930/extras/fdf72a14316961869040fae14f17bcb1.avif?t=1733876059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311930/extras_big/fdf72a14316961869040fae14f17bcb1.avif?t=1733876059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入皇家宫殿的壮丽，享受大王棋盘套装，灵感来自国际象棋的发源地—印度。此套装包含9套豪华棋盘，每套都由最优质的材料制成，从纹理丰富的木材到象牙和骨料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 大王棋盘套装的每个版本都是工艺与优雅的象征，展现了风格和材料的多样性，反映出国际象棋的永恒之美。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311930/extras/336b0f1703442afb7a5f8d108a5502b1.avif?t=1733876059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311930/extras_big/336b0f1703442afb7a5f8d108a5502b1.avif?t=1733876059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将大王宫廷的辉煌带到你的棋盘上，像皇室一样体验棋艺！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语",
